<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio | Web Developer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Hi, I'm <span class="highlight"><%= name %></span>.</h1>
        <p>A Web Developer specializing in clean code and functional design.</p>
        <a href="#projects" class="btn">View My Work</a>
    </header>

    <main class="page-container">

        <section id="about" class="container">
            <div class="about-hero">
                <h2>About <span class="highlight">Bipin</span></h2>
                <p>Building the web, one route at a time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="bio-text">
                    <h3>My Story</h3>
                    <p>バックエンドのロジックとフロントエンドの開発に興味を持つWebエンジニアです。
                    Node.jsでポートフォリオを構築し、ExpressやEJSなどの技術を学びながら、
                    保守性の高いコードを書くことを大切にしています。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skills-container">
                    <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
                    <ul class="skills-list">
                        <li class="skill-tag">Next.js/React</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">Node.js</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">Express</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">EJS</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">JavaScript (ES6)</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">CSS3 / Flexbox</li>
                        <li class="skill-tag">Git & GitHub</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Technical Projects</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">

                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Full-Stack Personal Portfolio</h3>
                    <p><strong>Stack:</strong> Node.js, Express, EJS, Git, Render</p>
                    <p>A server-side rendered application featuring dynamic routing and automated CI/CD deployment.</p>
                    <div class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="/" class="link">View Live</a>
                        <a href="https://memoapp-8eb2.onrender.com/" class="link secondary">Source Code</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Task Management System</h3>
                    <p><strong>Stack:</strong> JavaScript (ES6), LocalStorage/MongoDB</p>
                    <p>A productivity tool designed to manage school assignments and daily tasks. (Under Development)</p>
                    <span class="status-badge">Upcoming</span>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Get In Touch</h2>
            <p>I'm currently looking for new opportunities!</p>
            <div class="contact-buttons">
                <a href="mailto:bipin@email.com" class="btn">Email Me</a>
                <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="btn">+1 (234) 567-890</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>